<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Abu Dabbab</title>
    <style>
        .back{
            font-size: 27px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
        .paragraph{
            font-size: 25px;
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
        .translation-btn-usa{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1300px;
        }
        .translation-btn-ro{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1390px;
        }
        .invisible{
            display: none;
            top: -1000000px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .paragraph{
                font-size: 25px;
                width: 280vw;
            }
        }
        .image-end-1{
            position: relative;
            cursor: pointer;
            height: 340px;
            width: 380px;
            margin: 40px;
            box-shadow: 10px 10px 5px #aaaaaa;
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-image: url("https://www.karpaten.ro/media/cache/big_image/images/hotel/10750/s3-malikia-resort-abu-dabbab-ex-sol-y-mar-268885.jpg");
        }
        .dark{
            background-color: #333;
        }
        .image-end-1-big{
            z-index: 111;
            position: absolute;
            cursor: pointer;
            height: 540px;
            width: 880px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-left: 400px;
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-image: url("https://www.karpaten.ro/media/cache/big_image/images/hotel/10750/s3-malikia-resort-abu-dabbab-ex-sol-y-mar-268885.jpg");
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a class="back" href="/hurghada/home">     <p class="back">←</p>    </a>
    <div class="translation">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" class="translation-btn-usa" id="translation-btn-usa">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" class="translation-btn-ro" id="translation-btn-ro">
    </div>
    <h1>Abu Dabbab</h1>
    <div id="image-1-big" class="image-end-1-big invisible"></div>
    <p id="paragraph-ro" class="paragraph">
        Excursie de o zi cu snorkeling la broaștele țestoase din Abu Dabbab , alături de echipa noastră El Majico. Plecare va fi in jurul orei 6:00 in functe de hotel si o sa ajungem in jurul orei 9:00 .O sa inotam cu brostele testoase si o sa vedem corali si pestisorii viu colorati . 
        Broaște țestoase în habitatul lor natural - o experiență fabuloasă.
        <br><br>
        Include:<br>
        Masa de pranz va  fi bufet deschis și este inclusa .<br>
        Băuturi non alocolice ,fructe și dulciuri orientale.<br>
        Echipament de snorkeling.<br>
        <br><br>
        Pret:<br>
        50 € - 60 € variaza in functie de numarul de persoane<br>
        De preferat grup de  intre 8 si 11 persoane
        <br><br>
        Cand:<br>
        intreaba ghidul
    </p>
    <p id="paragraph-usa" class="paragraph invisible">
        A day trip with snorkeling to the turtles in Abu Dabbab, with our El Majico team.
        Departure will be around 6:00 depending on the hotel and we will arrive around 9:00. We will swim with the turtles and we will see brightly colored corals and fish. Turtles in their natural habitat.
        <br><br>
        Include:<br>
        Lunch will be open buffet and is included.<br>
        Non-alcoholic beverages, fruits and oriental sweets.<br>
        Snorkeling equipment.<br>
        <br><br>
        Price:<br>
        € 50 - € 60 varies depending on the number of people.<br>
        Preferably a group of between 8 and 11 people.
        <br><br>
        When:<br>
        asks the guide
    </p>
    <div class="images-section" id="images-section">
            <div id="image-1" class="image-end-1"></div>
    </div>
</body>
<script>

    const image1 = document.getElementById("image-1")
    const imageBig1 = document.getElementById("image-1-big")
    const body = document.querySelector("body")

    image1.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        imageBig1.classList.remove("invisible")
        body.classList.add("dark")
        image1.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    imageBig1.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        imageBig1.classList.add("invisible")
        body.classList.remove("dark")
        image1.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

    const translateBtnUsa = document.getElementById("translation-btn-usa")
    const translateBtnRo = document.getElementById("translation-btn-ro")
    const paragraphUsa = document.getElementById("paragraph-usa")
    const paragraphRo = document.getElementById("paragraph-ro")

    translateBtnUsa.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.remove("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    translateBtnRo.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.add("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

</script>
</html>